    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Copper cables run from these thick leather gloves to nodes that attach to the wearer\u2019s temples, allowing a spellcaster to convert the magic they normally cast to pure psychic intention. When you Cast a Spell using the *telekinetic converters*, you substitute any spoken words for simple thoughts, granting the subtle trait to the spell you\u2019re casting.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
